      <div class="card-label">My Inquiry Questions</div>
      <ul>
        <li>How did economic problems after the Great Depression contribute to the start of World War II?</li>
        <li>How did racism and nationalism influence the actions of Nazi Germany before and during WWII?</li>
        <li>Why did totalitarian governments gain support in Europe during the 1930s?</li>
        <li>How did propaganda affect people's attitudes and support for war during WWII?</li>
        <li>Why did Canada join World War II, and what impacts did the war have on Canadians?</li>
        <li>What were the social, economic, and political impacts of WWII on Canada and the world?</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
